# AI BTC Dev Frontend - Design System Transformation Rules

## Overview
Follow this comprehensive guide when updating any component to align with the AI BTC Dev design system. This ensures consistent theming, modern aesthetics, and maintainable code across the entire application.

## 1. Theme System Integration

### 1.1 Color Token Replacement
**ALWAYS** replace hardcoded colors with semantic theme tokens from `tailwind.config.ts`:

#### Background Colors
- `bg-[#121212]` → `bg-background`
- `bg-[#1A1A1A]` → `bg-background` (darker variant)
- `bg-[#2A2A2A]` → `bg-card`
- `bg-[#232325]` → `bg-card` (surface variant)

#### Text Colors
- `text-white` → `text-foreground`
- `text-gray-400`, `text-zinc-400` → `text-muted-foreground`
- `text-gray-300`, `text-zinc-300` → `text-muted-foreground`
- `text-gray-500`, `text-zinc-500` → `text-muted-foreground`

#### Accent Colors
- `text-orange-500`, `text-[#FF6B00]`, `text-[#FF4F03]` → `text-primary`
- `bg-orange-500/20` → `bg-primary/20`
- `border-orange-500/30` → `border-primary/30`
- `text-blue-500`, `text-[#0533D1]` → `text-secondary`
- `text-purple-400` → `text-secondary`

#### State Colors
- `text-red-500` → `text-destructive`
- `bg-red-500/20` → `bg-destructive/20`
- `border-red-500/30` → `border-destructive/30`

#### Border Colors
- `border-gray-600`, `border-zinc-700`, `border-zinc-800` → `border-border`

#### Muted Colors
- `bg-gray-600`, `bg-zinc-700` → `bg-muted`
- Use `text-muted` for very subtle text elements

### 1.2 Interactive States
- Active tabs/buttons: `bg-primary text-primary-foreground`
- Hover states: `hover:bg-muted/50`, `hover:text-foreground`, `hover:border-primary/50`
- Focus states: `focus:border-primary` with `transition-colors duration-150`

## 2. 12px Grid System Implementation

### 2.1 Spacing Scale (Multiples of 12px)
- `p-3` = 12px
- `p-4` = 16px  
- `p-6` = 24px ✓ (preferred for cards)
- `p-8` = 32px ✓ (preferred for main content)
- `p-12` = 48px ✓ (preferred for page containers)

### 2.2 Gap System
- `gap-3` = 12px
- `gap-4` = 16px
- `gap-6` = 24px ✓ (preferred for layouts)
- `gap-8` = 32px ✓ (preferred for major sections)

### 2.3 Margin System
- `mb-3` = 12px
- `mb-4` = 16px
- `mb-6` = 24px ✓ (preferred for sections)
- `mb-8` = 32px ✓ (preferred for major sections)
- `mb-10` = 40px
- `mb-12` = 48px

### 2.4 Container Patterns
```jsx
// Page containers
<div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 py-12">

// Card content
<CardContent className="p-8"> // or p-6 for smaller cards

// Section spacing
<div className="space-y-8"> // or space-y-6 for smaller sections
```

## 3. Modern Card Styling

### 3.1 Card Structure
```jsx
<Card className="bg-card border-border shadow-sm"> // Add shadow-sm for elevation
  <CardHeader className="pb-6"> // Increase bottom padding
    <CardTitle className="text-xl font-bold text-foreground flex items-center gap-3">
      <Icon className="h-6 w-6 text-primary" />
      Title
    </CardTitle>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent className="pt-0"> // Remove top padding to connect with header
    {/* Content */}
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```

### 3.2 Border Radius Updates
- `rounded-md` → `rounded-xl` (more modern feel)
- `rounded-lg` → `rounded-xl` (consistency)
- Keep `rounded-full` for avatars and badges

### 3.3 Shadow System
- Remove complex shadows: `shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]`
- Use simple shadows: `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md`, `shadow-lg`

## 4. Typography & Icon Improvements

### 4.1 Heading Hierarchy
- Page titles: `text-2xl font-bold text-foreground`
- Section titles: `text-xl font-semibold text-foreground`
- Card titles: `text-lg font-semibold text-foreground`
- Subsection titles: `text-base font-medium text-foreground`

### 4.2 Icon Sizing
- Section headers: `h-6 w-6` (24px)
- Card headers: `h-5 w-5` (20px)
- Inline icons: `h-4 w-4` (16px)
- Small UI icons: `h-3 w-3` (12px)

### 4.3 Icon Colors
- Primary icons: `text-primary`
- Secondary icons: `text-muted-foreground`
- Interactive icons: `text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground`

## 5. Interactive Elements & Transitions

### 5.1 Transition Timing
- Standard: `transition-colors duration-150`
- Transforms: `transition-transform duration-150`
- Complex: `transition-all duration-150`

